    dc:description "FIGURES 8–13. 8. Miobdelus humilis sp. nov.: male, paratype. 9. Miobdelus taiwanensis taiwanensis: male. 10. Nelmanwasus ornatus: male. 11–12. Sphaerobulbus miwai comb. nov.: male, lectotype of Staphylinus (Xanthocypus) miwai and attached labels; male. 13. Naddia taiwanensis: female. Scale bar: 3 mm" ;
